result.name: Cafe R & C

reviews.text: Four stars for presentation and a very accommodating hosts. Superb artistry with their 3D iced latte.

Coffee is super cute. But opening times annoyed me. Wanted to go a second and third time during our HK stay. Second time it was closed (before official closing time so we went all the way there for a closed door), third time (last day in HK) we actually specially waited in the area until 12 (opening time according to their door) - still closed. Waited till 12.30 (opening time according to google maps) - now open but got sent out again because "opening 'around' 1pm". So only go there if you happen to be around Causeway Bay during the afternoon anyway, don't depend on their opening times.
The drink menu is so cute
They has the best chocolate ever, and the lemon cake is great too 😍
Delicious cake and coffee, cozy place. Love it.
